!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{charset: 'utf-8'}
    %title= current_page.data.title || 'Form Factor'
    %script{src: '//use.typekit.net/kog5srr.js'}
    :javascript
      try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'application'
    %link{href: '/favicon.png', rel: 'shortcut icon'}
    %link{href: '/apple-touch.png', rel: 'apple-touch-icon'}

  %body
    = yield
    %footer.footer.row
      .well.cell
        .g
          .g-b.g-b--m--1of2
            %h1.mtf.mbs Notes
            %p.prl
              This site gives you piecemeal snippets to build your own form
              library. For that reason, there is no <i>Download</i> button
              anywhere. Maintain and optimize your CSS the way you need to; only
              use what’s needed.
            %p.prl
              All <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> text are merely placeholders, and
              all <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> tags are omitted. It’s advisable
              to use both in order to make your forms bullet-proof. Nested
              <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>s and <code>&lt;input&gt;</code>s are
              preferred, unless CSS demands siblings.
          .g-b.g-b--m--1of2
            %h3.g-b--m--3of4.mtm.mbs.mhc Thanks
            %p.g-b--m--3of4.mhc.s-625
              All of the design &amp; code is original, but much of it is
              inspired by these articles / microsites:
            %ul.g-b--m--3of4.mhc
              %li= link_to 'Todd Parker’s CSS-only custom selects', 'http://filamentgroup.github.io/select-css/demo/', target: '_blank'
              %li= link_to 'Lynn Fisher’s <i>A Single Div</i>', 'http://a.singlediv.com/', target: '_blank'
              %li= link_to 'Keyboard-Only Navigation', 'http://www.nngroup.com/articles/keyboard-accessibility/', target: '_blank'
              %li= link_to 'Placeholders in Form Fields Are Harmful', 'http://www.nngroup.com/articles/form-design-placeholders/', target: '_blank'
      .well.cell.tac
        = link_to 'http://dangodesign.net', class: 'footer-logo', target: '_blank', title: 'A project by Drew Powers' do
          = partial 'assets/images/powers.svg'
        = link_to 'https://github.com/dangodev/FormFactor.io', class: 'footer-github', target: '_blank', title: 'Fork on GitHub' do
          = partial 'assets/images/github.svg'
